<title>USA: Shoney's holders approve TPI purchase.</title>
<headline>Shoney's holders approve TPI purchase.</headline>
<dateline>NASHVILLE, Tenn. 1996-08-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>Shoney's Inc said its shareholders had approved a plan to purchase nearly all the assets of TPI Enterprises Inc.</p>
<p>The company said in a statement late on Wednesday that an increase in authorized shares and certain amendments to the company's stock option plan also were approved by shareholders.</p>
<p>Shoney's purchase of TPI is expected to close on Sept 9. The TPI subsidiaries will be acquired in exchange for 5.6 million shares of Shoney's common stock plus an extra $10 million of Shoney's stock based on the average closing market price for the 10 trading days before the closing.</p>
<p>-- New York newsroom, (212) 859-1610</p>
